BC Confirm Password README

What is the BC Confirm Password extension?
================================

BC Confirm Password is a true eZ Publish extension
that provides a simple dynamic module view which prompts users
to confirm the current user password when trying to edit content objects.

BC Confirm Password version
=======================

The current version of BC Confirm Password is 0.1.0
Last Major update: May 6, 2015


