Requirements
============

The following requirements exists for using BC Confirm Password extension:

o eZ Publish version:

  Make sure you use eZ Publish version 4.1 (required) or higher. eZ Publish 4.6.x+ (Community Build, 2011.11+) is recommended.

o eZ Publish kernel overrides:

  This extension requires kernel overrides in order to function. Please follow the installation instructions in detail.

o PHP version:

  Make sure you have PHP 5.x or higher.


Installation
============

o Install the extension

o Activate the extension

o Enable kernel class overrides in eZ Publish config.php by adding this line:

define( 'EZP_AUTOLOAD_ALLOW_KERNEL_OVERRIDE', true );

o Generate autoloads

o Generate kernel override autoloads

o Clear all caches


Usage - Module
============

o Login to admin

o Navigate to a content object

o Edit a content object

o Confirm password when prompted

o Continue using admin normally

Note: You can create a settings override of bcconfirmpassword.ini.append.php and customize the re-confirm password timeout limit by changing the number of minutes in the ReConfirmTimeInMinutes setting variable.


